high_descs: Turn to the left and walk to the side table.
Pick up the remote from the side table.
Step to the left and stand in front of the lamp.
Turn on the lamp with the remote.
anns.task_desc: With a remote turn on a lamp.

high_descs: Turn around, cross the room and turn right toward the small table.
Pick up the remote from the small table.
Turn left, go to the wall, turn right and look up at the lamp shade.
Turn off the light with the remote.
anns.task_desc: Turn off the lamp light with the remote.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the wall and then turn right to face the small table to the left of the couch.
Pick the remote up from the table.
Move to the left and face the lamp.
Turn the lamp to the left of the table off.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a remote and turn the lamp off.
